'''恆星大氣層'''是[[恆星|恆星]]的最外層區域，位置在[[太陽核心|核心]]、[[太陽#輻射層|輻射層]]和[[太陽#對流層|對流層]]之上，依照獨特的特徵可以分為數層：

* [[光球層|光球層]]是大氣層的最底層，也是我們能觀察到的大氣層中溫度最低的一層<ref name="BrightPS">{{Cite web|title="Beyond the Blue Horizon" – A Total Solar Eclipse Chase|url=http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/1999/08/990805111308.htm|accessdate=2010-05-21|date=1999-08-05|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/65LQDlJ4s?url=http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/1999/08/990805111308.htm|archive-date=2012-02-10|dead-url=no|quote=On ordinary days, the corona is hidden by the blue sky, since it is about a million times fainter than the layer of the sun we see shining every day, the photosphere.}}</ref>。來自恆星的[[光|光]]經由這一層從穿越更高的數層後，由恆星的表面逃逸入太空。[[太陽|太陽]]的光球層溫度為5700[[絕對溫度|K]]到5,780 K范围<ref name="lowTemp">{{Cite book|last1=Mariska|first1=J.T.|title=The solar transition region|series=Cambridge Astrophysics Series|url=http://www.cambridge.org/catalogue/catalogue.asp?isbn=9780521382618&ss=toc|publisher=Cambridge University Press|isbn=978-0-521-38261-8|access-date=2017-06-18|archive-date=2016-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160330055250/http://www.cambridge.org/catalogue/catalogue.asp?isbn=9780521382618|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="higherTemp">{{Cite book|last1=Lang|first1=K.R.|title=Sun, earth, and sky|url=https://archive.org/details/sunearthsky00lang_678|edition=2nd|date=September 2006|publisher=Springer|isbn=978-0-387-30456-4|page=[https://archive.org/details/sunearthsky00lang_678/page/n95 81]|chapter=5.1 MAGNETIC FIELDS IN THE VISIBLE PHOTOSPHERE|quote=this opaque layer is the photosphere, the level of the Sun from which we get our light and heat}}</ref>，[[星斑|星斑]]是光球層上受到[[磁場|磁場]]擾亂而溫度較低的區域<ref name="higherTemp" />。

* 在光球層之上的是[[色球層|色球層]]，這一層開始時的溫度會下降，然後隨著高度上升逐漸增溫至光球層的10倍左右。

* 在色球層之上還有[[過渡區|過渡區]]，在這裡溫度在約100公里的距離內迅速的增加至百萬K<ref>{{Cite book|last1=Mariska|first1=J.T.|title=The solar transition region|isbn=978-0-521-38261-8|page=60|quote=100 km suggested by average models}}</ref>。

* 在這之上就是恆星大氣層的外圍部份，是由非常稀薄但極端高溫(百萬K)的[[等離子體|電漿]]構成的[[冕_(恆星大氣層)|星冕]]<ref>{{Cite journal|title=The Temperature of the Low Corona During Solar Cycles 21–23|author=R.C. Altrock|date=2004|journal=Solar Physics|doi=10.1007/s11207-005-6502-4|volume=224|page=255|bibcode=2004SoPh..224..255A}}</ref>，[[過渡區|過渡區]]和[[冕_(大氣層)|星冕]]是在[[主序星|主序帶]]上所有的[[恆星|恆星]]都有的外觀。但不是所有演化中的恆星都是如此，看起來只有一些[[巨星|巨星]]和極少數的[[超巨星|超巨星]]才有[[冕_(恆星大氣層)|星冕]]。在[[天體物理學|天體物理學]]中尚待待解決的問題是星冕是如何被加熱到如此高的溫度？答案可能在恆星的[[磁場|磁場]]上，但確切的機制依然還沒有被清楚了解<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Sun's Corona – Introduction|url=http://imagine.gsfc.nasa.gov/docs/science/mysteries_l1/corona.html|accessdate=2010-05-21|publisher=[[美国国家航空航天局|NASA]]|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/65LQENcHi?url=http://imagine.gsfc.nasa.gov/docs/science/mysteries_l1/corona.html|archive-date=2012-02-10|dead-url=no|quote=Now most scientists believe that the heating of the corona is linked to the interaction of the magnetic field lines.}}</ref>。

以[[太陽|太陽]]為例，當[[日全食|日全食]]之際，太陽的光球層被遮蔽時，大氣層中的其他層次便被顯露出來<ref name="BrightPS" />。在這種情況下，色球層呈現出略帶粉紅色的圓弧<ref>{{Cite book|last1=Lewis|first1=J.S.|title=Physics and chemistry of the solar system|url=https://archive.org/details/physicschemistry00lewi_433|publisher=Elsevier Academic Press|edition=Second|date=2004-02-23|isbn=978-0-12-446744-6|quote=The dominant color is influenced by the [[Balmer_series|Balmer radiation]] of atomic hydrogen|page=[https://archive.org/details/physicschemistry00lewi_433/page/n101 87]}}</ref>，而[[日冕|日冕]]（太陽的星冕）像裝了一簇纓球的光暈。在[[食雙星|食雙星]]同樣的現象可以讓巨星的色球層可見<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Only Binary Stars Can Help Us Actually SEE a Stellar Chromosphere|url=https://www.cambridge.org/core/product/identifier/S1743921307006163/type/journal_article|last=Griffin|first=R. Elizabeth|date=2006-08|journal=Proceedings of the International Astronomical Union|issue=S240|doi=10.1017/S1743921307006163|volume=2|pages=700–705|language=en|issn=1743-9213}}</ref>。

